menaiki penerbangan kelas pertama.

479
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:45,440
Fikirkanlah,
jika kamu berdua benar-benar serasi,

480
00:26:46,060 --> 00:26:49,720
anda mungkin anak anjing pertama
yang dapat menerbangkan kapal terbang.

481
00:26:52,080 --> 00:26:53,280
Bersumpah awak tak tiru saya.

482
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:55,080
Apa?!

483
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:56,280
Meniru, dasar bodoh.

484
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:57,920
Ia langsung tidak berkaitan.

485
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:00,160
